ATF contains less detergents than motor oil.  Unfortunatly, it's an old
wives tale that has survived (like taking the thermostat and flaps out of
the vw).  I've worked in the oil industry for 7 years now, and you'd be
amazed at how many wives tales are out there.
:-)

